<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Básico on memoria digital</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/categories/b%C3%A1sico/</link><description>Recent content in Básico on memoria digital</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>es-es</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://volteret4.github.io/notas/categories/b%C3%A1sico/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Archivos Modificados Recientemente</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/archivos-modificados-recientemente/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/archivos-modificados-recientemente/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Muestra archivos modificados en el último día&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">find /ruta/a/tu/directorio -type f -mtime -1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">#Esto listará los archivos con detalles como permisos, propietario, tamaño y fecha de modificación.&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">find /ruta/a/tu/directorio -type f -mmin -60 -ls
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Automatic Installation Vim Plug</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/automatic-installation-vim-plug/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/automatic-installation-vim-plug/</guid><description>&lt;p> &lt;a class="link" href="https://junegunn.github.io/vim-plug/tips/automatic-installation/#automatic-installation" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Origen&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="vim-script">&lt;a class="link" href="https://junegunn.github.io/vim-plug/tips/automatic-installation/#vim-script" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Vim script&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Place the following code in your .vimrc before plug#begin() call, and Vim will automatically install vim-plug and the plugins when you open Vim.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-vim" data-lang="vim">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">let&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">data_dir&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">has&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;nvim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> ? &lt;span class="nx">stdpath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;data&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> . &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;/site&amp;#39;&lt;/span> : &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;~/.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">empty&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">glob&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">data_dir&lt;/span> . &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;/autoload/plug.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">silent&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">execute&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;!curl -fLo &amp;#39;&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="nx">data_dir&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">autocmd&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">VimEnter&lt;/span> * &lt;span class="nx">PlugInstall&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">--&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">sync&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">source&lt;/span> $&lt;span class="nx">MYVIMRC&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">endif&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c">&amp;#34; An example of vim-plug section ---------------------------------------------&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">call&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">plug&lt;/span>#&lt;span class="nx">begin&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">Plug&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;junegunn/seoul256.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">call&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">plug&lt;/span>#&lt;span class="nx">end&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">silent&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">!&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">colorscheme&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">seoul256&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="lua-script-equivalent-for-neovim">&lt;a class="link" href="https://junegunn.github.io/vim-plug/tips/automatic-installation/#lua-script-equivalent-for-neovim" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Lua script equivalent for Neovim&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-lua" data-lang="lua">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">local&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">data_dir&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim.fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">stdpath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;data&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim.fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">empty&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">vim.fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">glob&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data_dir&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">..&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;/site/autoload/plug.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">then&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">vim.cmd&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;silent !curl -fLo &amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">..&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">data_dir&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">..&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;/site/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">vim.o&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">runtimepath&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim.o&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">runtimepath&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">vim.cmd&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;autocmd VimEnter * PlugInstall --sync | source $MYVIMRC&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">end&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">-- An example of vim-plug section --------------------------------------------&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">local&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">local&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">Plug&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">vim.fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;plug#&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">vim.call&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;plug#begin&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">Plug&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;junegunn/seoul256.vim&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">vim.call&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;plug#end&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">vim.cmd&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;silent! colorscheme seoul256&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Crear Links De Archivos</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-links-de-archivos/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-links-de-archivos/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="tldr-link-archivos">Tldr link archivos
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ln -s archivo_original link &lt;span class="c1"># soft link&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ln archivo_original link
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Crear Multiples Archivos Oneline</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-multiples-archivos-oneline/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/crear-multiples-archivos-oneline/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Desactivar Servicio De Impresión</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/desactivar-servicio-de-impresi%C3%B3n/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/desactivar-servicio-de-impresi%C3%B3n/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/480082/how-to-disable-cups-service-on-reboot-with-systemd" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>stackexchange&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>Suelo conectarme a una red con muchas impresoras. Cuando se detectan impresoras, aparecen muchos mensajes molestos en GNOME. Uso la impresora rara vez, así que preferiría mantener CUPS desactivado la mayor parte del tiempo. Detener CUPS funciona y elimina las notificaciones molestas:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl stop cups
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Me gustaría desactivarlo al arrancar. Sorprendentemente, después de desactivarlo,&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl disabled cups
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>CUPS sigue ejecutándose después de reiniciar. El commando de estado&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl status cups
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Grep</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/grep/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/grep/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="usar-variables-en-grep">Usar variables en grep
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -io
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="búsqueda-en-una-carpeta-no-recursiva">&lt;strong>Búsqueda En una carpeta (no recursiva)&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/*
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Esto buscará &lt;code>&amp;quot;tu_string&amp;quot;&lt;/code> en todos los archivos dentro de la carpeta, pero &lt;strong>no&lt;/strong> en subcarpetas.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="búsqueda-recursiva-en-subdirectorios">&lt;strong>Búsqueda Recursiva en subdirectorios&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -r &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>El flag &lt;code>-r&lt;/code> (o &lt;code>-R&lt;/code>) have que &lt;code>grep&lt;/code> busque recursivamente en todos los subdirectorios.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="mostrar-número-de-línea-en-los-resultados">&lt;strong>Mostrar Número de línea en los resultados&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -rn &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>-n&lt;/code>: Muestra el número de línea donde aparece el string.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="ignorar-mayúsculas-y-minúsculas">&lt;strong>Ignorar Mayúsculas y minúsculas&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -ri &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>-i&lt;/code>: Ignore diferencias entre mayúsculas y minúsculas.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="buscar-archivos-específicos-por-extensión">&lt;strong>Buscar Archivos específicos (por extensión)&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Si solo quieres buscar en archivos &lt;code>.txt&lt;/code>, usa:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -r &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/ --include&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;*.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="excluir-archivos-o-carpetas">&lt;strong>Excluir Archivos o carpetas&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Si quieres excluir ciertos archivos o carpetas:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -r &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/ --exclude-dir&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;logs&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Esto excluirá la carpeta &lt;code>logs&lt;/code> de la búsqueda.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="mostrar-solo-los-nombres-de-los-archivos-que-contienen-el-string">&lt;strong>Mostrar Solo los nombres de los archivos que contienen el string&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grep -rl &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>El flag &lt;code>-l&lt;/code> have que solo se muestren los nombres de los archivos que contienen la cadena, sin mostrar las líneas.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="usar">&lt;strong>Usar &lt;code>rg&lt;/code> (ripgrep) Para mayor velocidad&lt;/strong>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Si tienes &lt;code>ripgrep&lt;/code> (&lt;code>rg&lt;/code>) instalado, es mucho más rápido:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rg &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;tu_string&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /ruta/a/la/carpeta/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Hacer Referencia A Argumentos Especificos Del Comando Anterior</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/hacer-referencia-a-argumentos-especificos-del-comando-anterior/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/hacer-referencia-a-argumentos-especificos-del-comando-anterior/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Origen: ChatGPT&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>También puedes hacer referencia a argumentos específicos del comando anterior utilizando la sintaxis !:n, donde &amp;ldquo;n&amp;rdquo; es el número del argumento que deseas utilizar. Por ejemplo, si el comando anterior fue ls -l archivo.txt, puedes utilizar la siguiente sintaxis para imprimir el nombre del archivo:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">echo !:2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Insertar Url En Foro</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/insertar-url-en-foro/</link><pubDate>Thu, 31 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/insertar-url-en-foro/</guid><description>&lt;p>Usa este snippet para poder insertar enlaces en foros&lt;/p>
