&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Atuin Historial Del Terminal Con Superpodéres</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/atuin-historial-del-terminal-con-superpod%C3%A9res/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/atuin-historial-del-terminal-con-superpod%C3%A9res/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Desactivar Mayúsculas</title><link>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/desactivar-may%C3%BAsculas/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://volteret4.github.io/notas/p/desactivar-may%C3%BAsculas/</guid><description>&lt;p>Desactiva Capslock:
